<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sec disp-level="2" class="sec">
 <div class="title" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Thermal wind calculation</div>
 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The change in zonal wind in the upper troposphere from a temperature gradient anomaly can be approximated (
  <a rid="R38" ref-type="bibr" href="#R38">
   <span class="italic">38</span>
  </a>) as
  <div class="disp-formula">
   <div id="m4" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">Δ</span>
      <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">u</span>
      <span class="mo">=</span>
      <span class="mo">−</span>
      <div class="mfrac">
       <div class="mrow">
        <div class="msub">
         <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">R</span>
         <span class="mtext">air</span>
        </div>
       </div>
       <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">f</span>
      </div>
      <span class="mtext">ln</span>
      <span stretchy="true" class="mo">(</span>
      <div class="mfrac">
       <div class="mrow">
        <div class="msub">
         <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">p</span>
         <span class="mn">0</span>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="mrow">
        <div class="msub">
         <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">p</span>
         <span class="mn">300</span>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <span stretchy="true" class="mo">)</span>
      <div class="mfrac">
       <div class="mrow">
        <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">d</span>
        <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">T</span>
       </div>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">d</span>
        <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">y</span>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </p>
 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">With the Coriolis frequency at the midlatitudes 
  <span class="italic">f</span> = 10
  <span class="sup">−4</span> s
  <span class="sup">−1</span>, the specific gas constant for air 
  <span class="italic">R</span>
  <sub>air</sub> = 287 m
  <span class="sup">2</span> s
  <span class="sup">−2</span> K
  <span class="sup">−1</span>, a surface pressure of 
  <span class="italic">p</span>
  <sub>0</sub> = 1000 mbar, an upper tropospheric pressure of 
  <span class="italic">p</span>
  <sub>300</sub> = 300 mbar, and a meridional temperature gradient anomaly of 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="m5" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <div class="mfrac">
       <div class="mrow">
        <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">d</span>
        <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">T</span>
       </div>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">d</span>
        <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">y</span>
       </div>
      </div>
      <span class="mo">=</span>
      <div class="mfrac">
       <span class="mn">0.5</span>
       <span class="mn">10</span>
      </div>
      <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">K</span>
      <span class="mo">°</span>
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
      <span class="mtext">lat</span>
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
      <span class="mo">=</span>
      <span class="mn">4.5</span>
      <span class="mo">×</span>
      <div class="msup">
       <span class="mn">10</span>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span class="mo">−</span>
        <span class="mn">7</span>
       </div>
      </div>
      <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">K</span>
      <span class="mo">/</span>
      <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">m</span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> (as observed over latitudes 55°N to 66°N in the T fingerprint; 
  <a ref-type="fig" rid="F1" href="#F1">Fig. 1A</a>), this would result in an approximate change in zonal winds of
 </p>
 <div class="disp-formula" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <div id="m6" class="math">
   <div class="mrow">
    <div class="mrow">
     <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">Δ</span>
     <span mathvariant="italic" class="mi">u</span>
     <span class="mo">=</span>
     <span class="mo">−</span>
     <span class="mn">1.6</span>
     <div class="msup">
      <span class="mtext">ms</span>
      <div class="mrow">
       <span class="mo">−</span>
       <span class="mn">1</span>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </div>
</sec>
